flowchart TD
    subgraph External["External systems"]
        ZohoInv[(Zoho Inventory / Books)]
        Authentik[Authentik OIDC]
    end

    ZohoGW[Zoho Integration Service\n192.168.1.205:8000]

    ZohoInv <-->|API via gateway| ZohoGW
    ZohoGW -->|PO sync / line items| PO[(purchase_orders\npo_lines)]

    PO --> Receive[Receive pills\nreceives + inventory_bags]
    QRPool[(qr_cards inventory\nRAW_BAG / VARIETY_PACK)]
    Receive -->|assign scan_token| QRPool
    Receive --> InvBags[inventory_bags\n+ batches RELEASED]

    Products[(products)]
    PAT[product_allowed_tablets]
    Products --> PAT
    PAT -.->|floor product picker| Floor

    InvBags --> Floor[Floor station\n/floor/token — scan bag QR]
    QRPool -.->|scanToken on label| Floor

    Floor --> WE[workflow_events\nappend-only]
    WE -->|pg_notify → projector| RM[Read models\nstation / bag / throughput]
    WE -->|finalize| FL[finished_lots\nfinished_lot_inputs]

    FL --> ZQ[zoho_assembly_ops queue]
    ZQ -->|dry-run / gated live| ZohoGW

    subgraph Admin["Admin UI — Authentik SSO"]
        ReceiveAdmin[Receive pills / inbound]
        QRAdmin[QR cards]
        ProdAdmin[Products + mappings]
        ZohoUI[Zoho operations UI]
        OutAdmin[Production output]
        Board[Floor board SSE]
    end

    Authentik -.->|protects| Admin
    ReceiveAdmin --> Receive
    QRAdmin --> QRPool
    ProdAdmin --> Products
    ProdAdmin --> PAT
    ZohoUI --> ZQ
    OutAdmin --> FL
    Board --> RM
